# WordForge AI - Project Overview

## Project Description
WordForge AI is a Vietnamese vocabulary learning application that uses AI to generate personalized learning content. The app features spaced repetition algorithms, interactive flashcards, and multiple exercise types to help users learn vocabulary effectively.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15.5.4 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Authentication**: NextAuth.js with Google OAuth
- **AI Integration**: Google Generative AI (Gemini)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with Radix UI components
- **State Management**: React hooks and context

## Key Features
- AI-generated vocabulary lessons and exercises
- Spaced repetition system (SuperMemo algorithm)
- Multiple exercise types: fill-in-the-blanks, matching, multiple choice
- Audio pronunciation support
- Progress tracking and review scheduling
- User authentication and personal decks

